 "Information..."
 "Snapshot"
 "UnSnapshot" KEY "U"
 "Leave Out"
 "Put Away"
 "Delete..." KEY "D"
 "Format Disk..."
 "Empty Trash"
 "ResetWB"
 "ToolsPrefs..."
